name: Spaceboy - Genesis
description:
The first of three Spaceboy music series with animated cover art, Genesis symbolizes the beginning of my journey into this new art form. Featuring Black Light, an original comic character of mine born from a combination of my childhood fandom.

Spaceboy is a homage to the visual vocabulary and audio aesthetics I love growing up. I composed the music to emulate chiptune sounds from classic video games with a touch of melancholia to evoke a sense of nostalgia.
